  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The present study aims to evaluate the impact of a weaning strategy based on identification
      of early signs of respiratory distress by lung ultrasound and the consequent implementation
      of a &quot;clinical optimization&quot; protocol as compared to usual care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
